description.zh-cn: 清朝康熙帝第十子。因参与九子夺嫡，被雍正帝革爵圈禁。乾隆帝即位后获释，封为辅国公。
description.en: The tenth son of the Kangxi Emperor of the Qing dynasty. He was stripped of his title and imprisoned by the Yongzheng Emperor for his involvement in the succession struggle of the nine princes. He was released after the Qianlong Emperor ascended the throne and was granted the title of Bulwark Duke.

description.zh-cn: 清朝第四位皇帝，清世祖顺治帝第三子，清朝统一中国后的第二位皇帝。
description.en: The fourth emperor of the Qing dynasty, the third son of the Shunzhi Emperor, and the second emperor of the Qing dynasty after the unification of China.

description.zh-cn: 康熙帝的贵妃，满洲镶黄旗人，太师、果毅公遏必隆之女，孝昭仁皇后之妹，皇十子允䄉的生母。
description.en: A Noble Consort of the Kangxi Emperor, from the Manchu Bordered Yellow Banner. She was the daughter of Grand Tutor and Duke Guoyi Ebilun, the younger sister of Empress Xiaozhaoren, and the birth mother of the emperor's tenth son, Yun'e.

description.zh-cn: 清朝第五位皇帝，清圣祖康熙帝第四子。
description.en: The fifth emperor of the Qing dynasty, the fourth son of the Kangxi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 清朝初年权臣，康熙帝四大辅臣之一，后金开国五大臣之一额亦都的第十六子。
description.en: An influential official in the early Qing dynasty, one of the Four Regents of the Kangxi Emperor, and the sixteenth son of Eidu, one of the five founding ministers of the Later Jin.

description.zh-cn: 后金开国五大臣之一。
description.en: One of the five founding ministers of the Later Jin dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 后金开国大汗努尔哈赤第四女，额亦都的妻子。
description.en: The fourth daughter of Nurhaci, the founding khan of the Later Jin dynasty, and the wife of Eidu.

description.zh-cn: 后金的建立者，后被其子皇太极追尊为清太祖。
description.en: The founder of the Later Jin dynasty, posthumously honored as Emperor Taizu of Qing by his son, Hong Taiji.

description.zh-cn: 康熙帝的第二位皇后，辅政大臣遏必隆之女。
description.en: The second empress consort of the Kangxi Emperor, daughter of the regent Ebilun.

description.zh-cn: 清朝宗室，康熙帝的嫡次子，曾被立为皇太子。
description.en: A member of the Qing imperial clan, the second son of the Kangxi Emperor, and was once the crown prince.

en: Prince Dun of the First Rank

description.zh-cn: 清朝的亲王爵位之一。
description.en: A title of nobility, specifically a Prince of the First Rank, in the Qing dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 清朝宗室，康熙帝第八子，九子夺嫡的核心人物之一。
description.en: A member of the Qing imperial clan, the eighth son of the Kangxi Emperor, and one of the central figures in the succession struggle of the nine princes.

description.zh-cn: 清朝贵族爵位，低于亲王、郡王，高于贝子。
description.en: A title of nobility in the Qing dynasty, ranking below a Prince of the First/Second Rank and above a Beizi.

description.zh-cn: 清朝宗室，康熙帝第九子，胤禩支持者。
description.en: A member of the Qing imperial clan, the ninth son of the Kangxi Emperor, and a supporter of Yinsi.

description.zh-cn: 清朝贵族爵位，低于贝勒，高于镇国公。
description.en: A title of nobility in the Qing dynasty, ranking below a Beile and above a Duke of the State.

description.zh-cn: 清朝宗室，康熙帝第十四子，雍正帝同母弟。
description.en: A member of the Qing imperial clan, the fourteenth son of the Kangxi Emperor, and a full brother of the Yongzheng Emperor.

en: Succession struggle of the nine princes

description.zh-cn: 清朝康熙皇帝晚年，其九位皇子争夺皇位的历史事件。
description.en: A historical event during the later years of the Kangxi Emperor of the Qing dynasty, where nine of his sons vied for the throne.

description.zh-cn: 清朝第六位皇帝，雍正帝第四子。
description.en: The sixth emperor of the Qing dynasty, the fourth son of the Yongzheng Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 清朝宗室爵位之一。
description.en: A title of nobility for members of the imperial clan in the Qing dynasty.

description.zh-cn: 清朝第三位皇帝，清太宗皇太极第九子。
description.en: The third emperor of the Qing dynasty, the ninth son of Hong Taiji.

description.zh-cn: 顺治帝之后妃，康熙帝的生母。
description.en: A consort of the Shunzhi Emperor and the birth mother of the Kangxi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 后金第二位大汗，清朝的开国皇帝。努尔哈赤第八子。
description.en: The second Khan of the Later Jin dynasty and the founding emperor of the Qing dynasty. The eighth son of Nurhaci.

description.zh-cn: 清太宗皇太极之妃，孝端文皇后之侄女，顺治帝的生母。
description.en: A consort of Hong Taiji, niece of Empress Xiaoduanwen, and the birth mother of the Shunzhi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 清朝官员，孝康章皇后之父，康熙帝外祖父。
description.en: An official of the Qing dynasty, father of Empress Xiaokangzhang, and maternal grandfather of the Kangxi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉的嫡福晋，阿巴噶右旗扎萨克多罗郡王乌尔彰噶喇普之女。
description.en: The primary consort of Yun'e, daughter of Urcenggarab, a Jasagh Doroi Junwang of the Abaga Right Banner.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉的继福晋，佐领常海之女。
description.en: The secondary consort of Yun'e, daughter of company captain Changhai.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉的媵妾，员外郎永保之女。
description.en: A concubine of Yun'e, daughter of Second class secretary Yongbao.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉的媵妾，护军校灵保之女。
description.en: A concubine of Yun'e, daughter of Sergeant Lingbao.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉第五子，生母为嫡夫人博尔济吉特氏。
description.en: The fifth son of Yun'e. His birth mother was the primary consort, Lady Borjigit.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉第六子，生母为庶母郭络罗氏。
description.en: The sixth son of Yun'e. His birth mother was the concubine, Lady Gorolo.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉是康熙帝的第十子。
description.en: Yun'e was the tenth son of the Kangxi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉的生母是温僖贵妃。
description.en: Yun'e's birth mother was Noble Consort Wenxi.

description.zh-cn: 因党附胤禩，允䄉被雍正帝革去爵位并圈禁。
description.en: Due to his alliance with Yinsi, Yun'e was stripped of his title and imprisoned by the Yongzheng Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 为避其兄雍正帝胤禛的名讳，胤䄉改名为允䄉。
description.en: To avoid the naming taboo of his elder brother, the Yongzheng Emperor (Yinzhen), Yin'e changed his name to Yun'e.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉是康熙帝第十子，雍正帝是康熙帝第四子，二人为兄弟关系。
description.en: Yun'e was the tenth son of the Kangxi Emperor, and the Yongzheng Emperor was the fourth son; they were brothers.

description.zh-cn: 温僖贵妃是遏必隆之女。
description.en: Noble Consort Wenxi was the daughter of Ebilun.

description.zh-cn: 遏必隆是额亦都之子。
description.en: Ebilun was the son of Eidu.

description.zh-cn: 遏必隆是穆库什之子。
description.en: Ebilun was the son of Mukushen.

description.zh-cn: 穆库什是努尔哈赤之女。
description.en: Mukushen was the daughter of Nurhaci.

description.zh-cn: 温僖贵妃是孝昭仁皇后的妹妹。
description.en: Noble Consort Wenxi was the younger sister of Empress Xiaozhaoren.

description.zh-cn: 孝昭仁皇后是康熙帝所册立的第二位皇后。
description.en: Empress Xiaozhaoren was the second empress consort of the Kangxi Emperor.

position.en: Prince Dun of the First Rank

description.zh-cn: 康熙四十八年（1709年），允䄉晋封为多罗敦郡王。
description.en: In 1709 (the 48th year of the Kangxi reign), Yun'e was promoted to Prince Dun of the First Rank.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉与皇八子胤禩交好，并结成同盟参与了对皇位的争夺。
description.en: Yun'e was on good terms with the eighth prince Yinsi and formed an alliance with him to contend for the throne.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉与皇九子胤禟结成同盟参与了对皇位的争夺。
description.en: Yun'e formed an alliance with the ninth prince Yintang to contend for the throne.

description.zh-cn: 允䄉与皇十四子允禵结成同盟参与了对皇位的争夺。
description.en: Yun'e formed an alliance with the fourteenth prince Yunti to contend for the throne.

description.zh-cn: 康熙晚年，允䄉参与了九子夺嫡事件。
description.en: During the later years of the Kangxi reign, Yun'e participated in the succession struggle of the nine princes.

description.zh-cn: 乾隆帝即位后命人释放允䄉，并重新封其为辅国公。
description.en: After ascending the throne, the Qianlong Emperor ordered the release of Yun'e and re-ennobled him as a Bulwark Duke.

description.zh-cn: 康熙帝是顺治帝之子。
description.en: The Kangxi Emperor was the son of the Shunzhi Emperor.

description.zh-cn: 康熙帝是孝康章皇后之子。
description.en: The Kangxi Emperor was the son of Empress Xiaokangzhang.

description.zh-cn: 顺治帝是皇太极之子。
description.en: The Shunzhi Emperor was the son of Hong Taiji.

description.zh-cn: 顺治帝是孝庄文皇后之子。
description.en: The Shunzhi Emperor was the son of Empress Xiaozhuangwen.

description.zh-cn: 皇太极是努尔哈赤之子。
description.en: Hong Taiji was the son of Nurhaci.

description.zh-cn: 孝康章皇后是佟图赖之女。
description.en: Empress Xiaokangzhang was the daughter of Tulai.
